        <abstract> 
<p>Sends the 1872 <hi rend="italic">Report</hi> of the U. S. Geological Survey of the Territories, for which he was zoologist.</p> 
            <p>Most American naturalists support CD. His study of ornithology convinced him.</p> 
<p><hi rend="italic">Lepus bairdii</hi> has a distribution limited to Yellowstone Lake.</p> 
            <p>No doubt CD knows of O. C. Marsh’s horse fossils.</p>
        </abstract>
